                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">shopman to Thomas Seely, of Tooley-street.</hi> I produce two gowns, three handkerchiefs, a petticoat, a scarf, two shifts, and some other things, pawned by the prisoner—I am sure he is the person.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18440408-name-854" type="witnessName">
