                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">shopman to James Telfer, pawnbroker</hi>, I have a gown, a shift, and petticoat, pawned by two females—the prosecutrix has identified them.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18440408-name-855" type="witnessName">
